E5%A1%98%E5%B0%8F%E8%91%89%E7%B8%BD-1476111599300493/?hc_ref=ARSQNPYzdZpZNbAQh9UgfF88wT67KtrbMnFV-jiTjKEgP8tT6svgrGU3xBWpt-FRYDQ</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我夠膽講，第一張圖將把劍當佩劍咁拎既係男人多過女人，成日行樓梯比人兜頭隊落黎，大部份都係男人<br />\n<br />\n利申：男人</blockquote><br />\nAgree <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n圖一真係見親都係男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不少年齡 廢老係街咁拎我都彈開少少<br />\n有次就係西裝友<br />\n都痴撚線 搭個電梯都爭啲俾佢隊到眼同面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隊到身之後都出聲叫佢拎好把遮 <br />\n屌佢老母 你估你當自己拎劍咩</blockquote><br />\n屌又係西裝友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係唔係同一個仆街黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e4439ebaa526c5b6747db3b06551bcc3168f49","tid":381602,"uid":57675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:25:39.000Z","msg":"喺九龍塘站放工時間見過一個阿伯以為自己好撚型咁用膊頭托住把遮<br />\n即係長遮個尖向上 又指向小小後面咁<br />\n仲要企喺電梯到落緊去都仲繼續托<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n托你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1d9fbfc4efdeeafbfb853aa6176fdbc0ef562d","tid":381602,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7122c8c378f0fe293836a6f45ee9569acfab0b","tid":381602,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf01c76ec0d314690fabf654112ae73cf3253bbd","tid":381602,"uid":22932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D仆街女人真係永遠唔會舉高把遮<br />\n落雨大家都開遮起馬有得同佢遮撞遮<br />\n出太陽班死港女係行人路多人果時都唔識收遮，又唔舉高<br />\n成把血滴子咁衝入人堆真係屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n我會直接用手推開佢把遮<br />\n咁就唔驚俾佢插到<br />\n<br />\n擔遮明明應該係一樣人人都識既野<